de.ityx.contex.itag.dao

Class LabelEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ityx.contex.itag.dao.LabelEntity

  • @Entity
public class LabelEntity
extends Object
    Database entity storing information about a single label. This is the entity class corresponding to the Label DTO. A LabelEntity contains the following fields:

    • id (database primary key) - an ID that is unique across all labels in the database. This ID may change during export and import. Not mapped in DTO.
    • profile - the master and namespace this label belongs to. Not mapped in DTO.
    • localid - the "namespace-local ID": This is a second ID that is unique across all labels belonging to the same (master, namespace) tuple. This ID stays the same during export and import. Corresponds to Label.getId() in DTO.
    • title - The human-readable description of the label. Corresponds to Label.getTitle() in DTO.
